DESCRIPTION:Join us for the next Renton Business Information Session on Tue
	sday\, April 2 from 3 to 4 p.m. at the Renton Library\, with a virtual opt
	ion available. This session will feature updates on the Renton Market\, Pa
	vilion\, and Piazza\, with the Pavilion project team sharing what business
	es can expect in the coming months and the latest information related to L
	egacy Square. These sessions are a great opportunity to stay informed\, as
	k questions\, and connect with the city and other members of the business 
	community as downtown Renton continues to grow and evolve. All Renton busi
	nesses are welcome. April 2 \\(first Thursday of the month\\) ⏰ 3–4 p.m. R
	enton Library \\(100 Mill Ave. S\\) Virtual option available https://us06w
